		"ItemTooltips"
		{
			"item_pipe"		"Awesome for saving birds vs high magic damage aoe lineups."
			"item_sheepstick"		"Another useful choice, mostly for cases when you need lockdown against BKB carrier or another disable for team."
			"item_bloodthorn"		"Perfect offensive item: crit, silence, attackspeed. a lot of damage."
			"item_hurricane_pike"		"Another defensive choice. Good stats, attack range, mobility. Altho, most of the time you won't need it."
			"item_ultimate_scepter"		"With new lvl 25 talent it's not as required as it used to be, but it still very good item for both offensive (additional familliar as damage) and defensive (additional stun and stats) purposes"
			"item_assault"		"Our general tool (after medallion-aghs) to amplify tankiness, tower damage, help our team with aura and just kill things faster."
			"item_shivas_guard"		"If you arenot going to pick up AC, it's probably another choice for you. Altho, while we want to get AC tight after aghs, shiva's will be our very last slot to get."
			"item_lotus_orb"		"And another one glimmer cape alternative, but this one is more like team-oriented and used only for it's purging part."
			"item_desolator"		"Offensive choice. No lockdown, but increases our -armor potential and damage vs towers. I pick it up mostly in cases when the game is already won."
			"item_blight_stone"		"One blight stone goes into medallion, another one just lies in our inventory to provide another -2 armor. Pretty useful, cheap, can be upgraded into deso later."
			"item_medallion_of_courage"		"One of the best ways for us to amplify our damage wth familliars. Also solves mana regen issues"
			"item_solar_crest"		"Use it on summoned catapult or familliar while pushing to instantly melt towers."
			"item_rod_of_atos"		"Cheap alternative for Bloodthorn or Sheepstick. Pretty cheap, gives Visage additional lockdown and tankiness"
			"item_glimmer_cape"		"Often you will be focused, so you won't survive and graekeeper's cloak won't help you. Glimmer Cape is actually pretty good at saving teammates or yourself, so it can be pretty good choice sometimes."
			"item_silver_edge"		"Against Tidehunter, Bristleback, Antimage aghs or if you need some kind of repositioning item"
			"item_aeon_disk"		"Against burst initiators and long disables (Faceless Void, Axe, Magnus)"
			"item_hand_of_midas"		"We need levels as fast as possible to get to this juicy level 12 powerspike. Until then there's not much point in getting something else since Cloak is enough for surviveability and Headdress is enough for sustain. Works well if the game will be delayed anyway and you had a decent lane"
			"item_guardian_greaves"		"Powerful aura and a lot of sustain. Usually you tend to not upgrade your boots as Visage for a long time, and Greaves work well with all this \"early pressure\" playstyle"
		}
	}
